      "citation_id": "[CITATION_2]",
      "span_text": "Beyond the US, the economic burden of AKI has been studied in England where the annual cost of AKI-related inpatient care has been estimated at $1.4 billion. In addition to incomplete procedure and hospital-level adjustment, this study is limited by its ascertainment of AKI and costs, which was extrapolated from 1 hospital region to the rest of England."
